{"tid":1799424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳廣場男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-12-27T03:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T03:53:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"706719411e554a5ec574369dc0f3b397400ac987","tid":1799424,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"一名45歲男子昨日在將軍澳廣場墮樓死亡，傳出巨響驚動保安員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n現場為將軍澳唐德街1號。警方昨晚6時27分接獲保安報案，指聽到巨響，其後發現事主倒臥平台，懷疑從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主當場被證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信從一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1668117/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E5%B7%A8%E9%9F%BF%E9%A9%9A%E5%8B%95%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%93%A1</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4d9157a8d8a5688fe0ec8de10cb6607d47e7a1b5","tid":1799424,"uid":39226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"沒有檢獲遺書又無可疑"},{"pid":"0c38acd30406a186698911018c6e4e5b3b9de022","tid":1799424,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46bac7e1060325a83ac4d159a7c0831cf7acfa","tid":1799424,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"又係將軍澳....."},{"pid":"52fd1133e28107b5ced31b2ba83d0af8f950d2ac","tid":1799424,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"又無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2558c2dc521c75c698b032c4843cd37d2a95739","tid":1799424,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"已經好多單係TKO<br />\n<br />\n<strong>路西法效應<br />\nTKO局的人見其他狗姦人殺人無後果而加入<br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"84fe5faf4a6fce44bc8a98594c23b3ae1b5a2227","tid":1799424